description:
The birth of baby Jesus is something most people think of with joy. But this occasion was actually brought about by the saddest day in Heaven. What happened between Lucifer and Michael on this tragic day? Was there really war in Heaven? Why was Lucifer cast out of Heaven? How did God feel about the turmoil that was a result of the battle in Heaven? 
 
In this Bible study, Francois DuPlessis examines the war in Heaven and the plan that arose because of this war. Why was baby Jesus' birth necessary? Why would Christ leave the glory and adoration of Heaven to come to the Earth to live a life of discomfort, deprivation, and difficulty? Discover God's immeasurable love for you.
